org.tagaprice.server.dao.helper
Class HibernateSaveEntityCreator

java.lang.Object
  org.tagaprice.server.dao.helper.HibernateSaveEntityCreator

public class HibernateSaveEntityCreator
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used for testing purposes only. Entities can freshly created, i.e. new objects will be created with each call, by calling the various create methods. This class is "hibernate session save" by only providing methods where you have to specify the identifier yourself. So if you create two objects with the same identifier it's your own fault.

Author:
"forste"
